<p>The number type supports the entry of currency values. The format
	options supported by the currency attribute affect the rendering/validate
	in the follow ways:</p>
<u>PageFlow</u>
<pre>
	&lt;rowScroller [row scroller options]&gt;
		&lt;attributeField title="<i>title</i>" subTitle="<i>sub title</i>" binding="<i>xpath binding</i>" /&gt;
 	&lt;/rowScroller&gt;
</pre>
<ul>
	<li><i>title</i> Title rendered at the top of the column.</li>
	<li><i>subTitle</i> Rendered below the main title.</li>
	<li><i>binding</i> xpath binding referring to an Attribute in the
		model to which this column is bound.</li>
</ul>
<u>Model</u>
<pre>
	&lt;attribute id="<i>id</i>" value="<i>value</i>" unit="<i>ISO Code</i>"format="number,[min=<i>min value</i>],[max=<i>max value</i>]&gt;
</pre>
<ul>
	<li><i>min</i> Used during validation to define the minimum value
		that will be accepted.</li>
	<li><i>max</i> Used during validation to define the maximum value
		that will be accepted.</li>
</ul>
